    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Nahoon is quite simply Uluwatu on a budget, in a mirror. It’s beautiful out there though. The waves are incredibly fun. My first one is the biggest that I get; a roundhouse into the foam and my fins almost lose control. I get a few more wraps after that and kick out. After an hour my brain starts playing the jaws music and I decide to to make avo rice cakes and a coffee in the carpark. ",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "Nahoon is quite simply Uluwatu on a budget, in a mirror. It’s beautiful out there though. The waves are incredibly fun. My first one is the biggest that I get; a roundhouse into the foam and my fins almost lose control. I get a few more wraps after that and kick out. After an hour my brain starts playing the jaws music and I decide to to make avo rice cakes and a coffee in the carpark. ",
