    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I go for a beautiful run down the beach. My body definitely knew that I had been sick for the last few days - so I kept it short and simple. Running down the beach in the Transkei is simply fucking beautiful. The ocean is alive. The beaches are endless, yet in a moment they dissipate and you’re trekking up some impossibly vertical sand dune into a beautiful milkwood forrest.",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "I go for a beautiful run down the beach. My body definitely knew that I had been sick for the last few days - so I kept it short and simple. Running down the beach in the Transkei is simply fucking beautiful. The ocean is alive. The beaches are endless, yet in a moment they dissipate and you’re trekking up some impossibly vertical sand dune into a beautiful milkwood forrest.",
