            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "I’m beginning to get really excited about the run with Damo next month. Holy shit it’s in a month. I cannot let myself get worked up about it though - I honestly think that I could do it tomorrow if I had to, it would be hard but possible. I’m going to do my best to use my legs everyday until then and be sure to rest and eat well. Rogue running in the Transkei is set to be… silly at the very least. ",
